4:
Hey, you're gonna get your clothes
dirty! Quit racing around!
9:
Look, look! Aren't I cute? Sisty bought
these clothes for me!
13:
Did she now... Hey, lookin' good,
small fry.
18:
You look very cute. Are you dressed
as Santa?
31:
"With a jolly laugh, Santa flew off into
the night in his sled pulled by
reindeer... The end."
37:
Those kids didn't do anything, but he
still got them candy and toys.
42:
That's right. And you know, Arum,
you might get something too.
53:
Th-that's right! He certainly is! I bet
you can't wait for the holidays now!
62:
Huh, who would've thought... Is he
some sort of sprite? The human
world sure is full of weird stuff.
79:
You know what? I wanna hand out
presents too!
83: What are you going on about now?
88: Well, I'm dressed for the part, aren't I?
91:
Just because you've got the look
doesn't mean you can do the job.
93:
What exactly do you plan on giving
people, anyway? Candy?
97: No way! My candy is all mine!
101:
Hm... What can I give people...
Ummm...
111:
I'll hold him off! Please... Leave now
while you can!
113: No, I won't leave you, Ted!
127: Here you go! A present, just for you!
130:
Uh, okay... Wait, what?! Where'd you
get an elemental gem, kid?
133:
Isn't it pretty? I got that in the
Kaleidoscope!
136:
A brat like you? What the heck are
you talking about? Who are you?
138:
Wait... Are you the Little Lady Fiend
everyone's talking about? They say if
you encounter her in the
Kaleidoscope, she'll help you out!
142: Huh? I'm just handing out presents.
146:
Uh... Could you just accept the gift? I
know it's a bit weird, but it IS the
holidays.
149:
I-I see... Well, thanks for your
helpand the gem, I suppose.
162:
Ahhh! Nothing better than a nice cold 
glass of milk after a hard day's work!
169:
Oh, if it isn't the Little Lady Fiend!
Thanks for your help the other day.
Here, have some candy!
172:
No problem! Here, you can have an
elemental gem in return!
175:
Nah, I don't need it. Gettin' more
charity from a youngin like you puts
a bad taste in my mouth. I
appreciate the thought, though.
177:
You're her big sister, right? I'd like
you to have these sweets!
178:
That little lady's helped us out more
times than I can count, so this is our
way of saying thanks! Hope you like
it!
185:
Hehe! I knew this was a good idea!
Look at all the treats we're getting!
187:
When I grow up, I wanna do this for
a living! What do you think, Lightsy?
195:
Hey, wait a minute... Can fiends
really become Santa? I thought the
guy in the story was some kind of
sprite.
199:
Um, well, here's the thing about
Santa...
204:
He's not real?! Wait, so now what do
I do? I spent all my money on that
costume!
207:
It'll be fine. We've already bought her
a present this year.
211:
Do you really think I'm gonna let you
be the only one getting her
something?
215:
Y-you're a strict one, huh? Don't
worry, we can work something out.
220:
I appreciate it. I had no idea this
whole Santa business was so
complicated...
226: Ahaha! Playing Santa is so much fun!
230:
Jeez... She has no clue what we're
going through...
233: ...She sure is a handful, isn't she?
